# ┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓
# ┃          Windowrules Configuration        ┃
# ┗━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┛

source = ~/.config/hypr/config/defaults.conf
source = ~/.config/hypr/active-colors.conf

# Windows Rules https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Window-Rules/ #

# Inhibit idle on fullscreen
windowrule = idleinhibit fullscreen, fullscreenstate: * 2

# Float Necessary Windows
windowrule = float, class:^(.*org.pulseaudio.pavucontrol.*)
windowrule = float, class:^()$,title:^(.*Picture in picture.*)$
windowrule = float, title:^(.*Picture-in-Picture.*)$
windowrule = float, class:^()$,title:^(.*Save File.*)$
windowrule = float, class:^()$,title:^(.*Open File.*)$
windowrule = float, class:^()$,title:^(.*Export.*)$
windowrule = float, class:^(LibreWolf)$,title:^(.*Picture-in-Picture.*)$
windowrule = float, class:^(xdg-desktop-portal-gtk|xdg-desktop-portal-kde|xdg-desktop-portal-hyprland)(.*)$
windowrule = float, class:^(polkit-gnome-authentication-agent-1|hyprpolkitagent|org.org.kde.polkit-kde-authentication-agent-1)(.*)$
windowrule = float, class:^(CachyOSHello)$
windowrule = float, class:^(zenity)$
windowrule = float, class:^()$,title:^(Steam - Self Updater)$
windowrule = float, class:^(org.gnome.Loupe)$
windowrule = center, class:^(org.gnome.Loupe)
windowrule = float, class:^io.missioncenter.MissionCenter$
windowrule = center, class:^io.missioncenter.MissionCenter$
windowrule = size 50% 65%, class:^io.missioncenter.MissionCenter$
windowrule = float, class:^Bitwarden$
windowrule = center, class:^Bitwarden$
windowrule = size 40% 65%, class:^Bitwarden$
windowrule = float, class:^(localsend)$
windowrule = size 25% 55%, class:^(localsend)$
windowrule = center, class:^(localsend)$


windowrule = float, class:^de.haeckerfelix.Shortwave$
windowrule = move 51% 5%, class:^de.haeckerfelix.Shortwave$
windowrule = size 750 550, class:^de.haeckerfelix.Shortwave$

# Hyprprop
windowrulev2 = float, title:^(hyprprop)$
windowrulev2 = center, title:^(hyprprop)$
windowrulev2 = size 800 600, title:^(hyprprop)$

# Allow screen tearing
windowrule = immediate, class:^(cs2)$
windowrule = immediate, class:^(rivals)$

# Increase the opacity
windowrule = opacity 0.92, class:^(thunar|nemo)$
windowrule = opacity 0.96, class:^(discord|armcord|webcord)$
windowrule = opacity 0.8, class:^(Alacritty|foot)$
windowrule = opacity 0.95, title:^(QQ|Telegram)$
windowrule = opacity 0.95, title:^(NetEase Cloud Music Gtk4)$

# Border Colors
windowrule = bordercolor $busy_border, title:^(.*Copying files.*)$
windowrule = bordercolor $busy_border, title:^(.*Confirm File Replacing.*)$
windowrule = bordercolor $busy_border, title:^(.*pacman.*)$
windowrule = bordercolor $busy_border, title:^(.*paru.*)$
windowrule = bordercolor $busy_border, title:^(.*p - p.*)$
windowrule = bordercolor $busy_border, title:^(.*yay.*)$

# General window rules
windowrule = size 960 540, title:^(.*Picture-in-Picture.*)$
windowrule = move 25%-, title:^(.*Picture-in-Picture.*)$
windowrule = float, title:^(imv|mpv|danmufloat|termfloat|nemo|ncmpcpp)$
windowrule = move 25%-, title:^(imv|mpv|danmufloat|termfloat|nemo|ncmpcpp)$
windowrule = size 50% 50%, title:^(imv|mpv|danmufloat|termfloat|nemo|ncmpcpp)$
windowrule = animation popin, class:^(kitty|Alacritty|foot)$
windowrule = animation slide down, workspace:^(special:terminal)
windowrule = animation slide left, workspace:^(special:music)
windowrule = noblur, class:^(org.mozilla.firefox)$

# Floating windows on workspaces 1 to 10
windowrule = bordercolor $floating_border, floating:1
windowrule = rounding 10, floating:1

# Pinned Borders
windowrule = bordercolor $pinned_border, pinned:1

# Xwayland Borders
windowrule = bordercolor $xwayland_border, xwayland:1

# Special Workspaces Borders
windowrule = bordercolor $special_border1 $special_border2 180deg, onworkspace:s[1]

# HyprMode - Float and center (for Alacritty/Kitty)
windowrule = stayfocused, class:(hyprmode)
windowrule = float, class:(hyprmode)
windowrule = center, class:(hyprmode)
windowrule = size 767 655, class:(hyprmode)
windowrule = opacity 0.95, class:(hyprmode)

# OSTT Speech to Text
windowrule = stayfocused, title:ostt
windowrule = float, title:ostt
windowrule = size 14% 10%, title:ostt
windowrule = move 85% 89%, title:ostt
windowrule = bordercolor $busy_border, title:ostt


# Windows Rules End #

# Workspaces Rules https://wiki.hyprland.org/Configuring/Workspace-Rules/ #
workspace = special:terminal, on-created-empty:[float] $terminal, persistent:false
workspace = special:music, on-created-empty: [float]$spotify && $radio, persistent:false
workspace = special:todo, on-created-empty: [float]$ticktick, persistent:false
workspace = special:stash, persistent:true


# Workspaces Rules End #

# Layers Rules #
#Rofi
layerrule = blur, ^rofi$
layerrule = blurpopups, ^rofi$
layerrule = ignorealpha 0.5, ^rofi$


# Walker
layerrule = animation popin ^walker$
layerrule = blur, ^walker$
layerrule = blurpopups, ^walker$
layerrule = ignorealpha 0.5, ^walker$
layerrule = xray 0, ^walker$

layerrule = animation fade, ^selection$

# Layers Rules End #
